                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Loomis</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-11-01"><hi rend="italic">November 1,
                                1899</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Puerto Cabello formally and probably effectively blockaded by Castro
                            Government.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Loomis.</hi></signed></closer>
